metadata.name: Skelet Guy #1
metadata.description: 10 000 Skelet Guys are scattered among the nine circles of the underworld, each one different from the other, the circle they are in represents their truth, by completing the tests of the ninth level they will take the image of their soul, the image of their true self.  After four clicks of traveling through the Mictlan, the etherium blockchain will be your final destination!
